s since has been more of a surprise.\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1493, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1346, \"end\": 1356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.981803457608675, \"rank\": 0.018533793347689995, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 1369, \"end\": 1374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998603926, \"rank\": 1.3971821370360082e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1423, \"end\": 1428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9261847302836232, \"rank\": 0.07969756169537189, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1341}, {\"ngram\": \"serious challengers\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1397}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1406}, {\"ngram\": \"the emergence\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1448}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1458}, {\"ngram\": \"a surprise\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Matthew Hudson-Smith has put years of injury woe, not to mention the \\u00admental health struggles that had him contemplating suicide, behind him to become the fastest man on the planet over 400m.Molly Cauderyis also a world No1, in the pole vault, though her form has dipped a little.\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1495, \"end\": 1515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hudson-Smith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matthew Hudson-Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hudson-Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hudson-Smith\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1529}, {\"ngram\": \"injury woe\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1543}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\u00admental health struggles\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1588}, {\"ngram\": \"suicide\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1623}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest man\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1661}, {\"ngram\": \"the planet\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"Molly Cauderyis also a world No1\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1718}, {\"ngram\": \"the pole vault\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1737}, {\"ngram\": \"her form\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Things have never quite gone right for heptathlete Katarina \\u00adJohnson-Thompson at the Olympics and she again comes in under something of an fitness cloud, but knowing she can contend after\\u00ad \\u00adregaining her world title last year.\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 2003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Things\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1783}, {\"ngram\": \"heptathlete Katarina\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1836}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00adJohnson-Thompson\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1854}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1870}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1909}, {\"ngram\": \"an fitness cloud\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1929}, {\"ngram\": \"after\\u00ad\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1965}, {\"ngram\": \"her world title\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 1992}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jemma Reekieand 17-year-old Phoebe Gill could ensure Hodgkinson is not alone on the 800m podium, while the relays again promise to offer fertile ground.\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2005, \"end\": 2010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jemma_Redgrave\", \"score\": 0.9999999999067768, \"rank\": 9.344814086260114e-